{"tid":1369302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新晉耶撚既禱告","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:44:03.000Z","uid":89538,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"018088ab3a663337c7a53ac53334c1198c220a69","tid":1369302,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"親愛的天父上帝,<br />\n<br />\n聽日 相信已經有好多人下定左決心<br />\n用自己既生命去保護香港捍衛自己家園<br />\n一群有熱誠有理想<br />\n未來充滿無限可能既年青人可以要作出犧牲<br />\n卑微無能既我 只能係度向萬能既上帝作一個禱告<br />\n希望當大家害怕憤怒傷心難過既時候 陪伴住我地 讓我地既心靈得以可以依靠<br />\n希望當大家無助困惑辛苦迷惘既時候 可以指引我地路向<br />\n希望主可以帶領我地走過呢一個難關<br />\n用佢既愛去守護我地每一位 保護我地不受魔鬼既傷害<br />\n祈求香港可以有一日回到大家自由歡欣安居樂業既時候<br />\n<br />\n奉我主耶穌基督得勝既名字祈求<br />\n呀門<br />\n<br />\n祝大家武運昌隆"},{"pid":"9e51694c76c7fbd6102e6b6c70fb488067a9b963","tid":1369302,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155364e5fb7784830127523db71a75214279fc26","tid":1369302,"uid":270506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"Sing Hallelujah to the lord"},{"pid":"29ae562f63b9babf02532989da74c7abc85bd6bc","tid":1369302,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c7b5d45e3413d01132759554091e32b3d0dd0f","tid":1369302,"uid":96696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"係基督徒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d313d6ee232670479478f379d1c4ee779aaee26","tid":1369302,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3f3b373955a83e6747892e8d5c96bc1ec1204b4","tid":1369302,"uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以係呢個post找到一點安寧<br />\n主永遠都